{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.760", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.560", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mittlerweile ist es 13\u00a0Minuten nach zw\u00f6lf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.080", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft im Klartext: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.680", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gestern vor 32\u00a0Jahren explodierte der Block\u00a04 des AKW Tschernobyl. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.080", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis heute dauern die katastrophalen Folgen an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis heute verschlingen die Aufr\u00e4umarbeiten allein in Tschernobyl viele Milliarden Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.840", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tausende Menschen sind an den Folgen der Radioaktivit\u00e4t gestorben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.560", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hunderttausende wurden evakuiert und verloren f\u00fcr immer ihre Heimat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.240", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "32\u00a0Jahre nach Tschernobyl und 7\u00a0Jahre nach der Atomkatastrophe von Fukushima sind in Deutschland noch immer sieben Atommeiler am Netz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und noch immer kann auch hier jederzeit ein Super-GAU passieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sollten wir nicht vergessen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.240", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Atomausstieg hat angefangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber er ist noch nicht abgeschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.200", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das geh\u00f6rt einfach zur Wahrheit dazu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erst vorvorgestern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.800", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am Dienstag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.520", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat der BUND eine Studie \u00fcber die Unsicherheiten deutscher Atommeiler vorgelegt und zahlreiche M\u00e4ngel aufgef\u00fchrt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.120", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr M\u00f6ring hat das ja gerade schon angesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.040", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Studie zufolge gibt es keine ausreichenden Katastrophenschutzpl\u00e4ne. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.960", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Schutzstandards bei Hochwasser, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.280", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erdbeben und Anschl\u00e4gen sind mangelhaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.520", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Physikerin Oda Becker, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.920", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Autorin der Studie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warnt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich zitiere\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.600", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eFehler im Reaktorkern werden nur per Zufall gefunden\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.800", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist alarmierend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.720", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "finde ich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Studie wird festgestellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.240", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sicherheitsrelevante technische Ma\u00dfnahmen nicht mehr erfolgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.840", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sich das f\u00fcr die Betreiber angesichts der geplanten Abschaltungen bis 2021/2022 nicht mehr lohnt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Profitsystem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.560", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das sollte alarmieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hubert Weiger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.000", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Vorsitzende des BUND, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.240", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kritisiert die Unt\u00e4tigkeit von Bund und L\u00e4ndern zutreffend\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.400", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zitat\u00a0\u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.560", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Politik ist das wirtschaftliche Interesse der Betreiber wichtiger als die Sicherheit der Bev\u00f6lkerung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.320", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linken unterst\u00fctzen die Schlussfolgerung des BUND nach sofortigem Atomausstieg und Novellierung des Atomgesetzes. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.680", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es auch richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.040", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Ministerium umgehend zu dieser BUND-Studie mit diesen alarmierenden Nachrichten Stellung nehmen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.440", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit da Klarheit hergestellt wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie mich jedoch noch eines sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.680", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kritik des BUND richtet sich nicht nur an die Bundesregierung und die Atomaufsicht in Bayern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die die M\u00e4ngel im Reaktorblock Gundremmingen\u00a0C nicht zum Anlass nimmt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Meiler abzuschalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.920", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie die Gr\u00fcnen in ihrem Antrag zu Recht fordern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.240", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kritik des BUND an deutschen Atomkraftwerken ist zu Recht auch auf Reaktoren in den \u00fcbrigen Bundesl\u00e4ndern gem\u00fcnzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.560", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "richtet sich also auch an die Bundesl\u00e4nder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.000", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen die Atomministerien gr\u00fcn gef\u00fchrt sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.880", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier gibt es viel Luft nach oben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ich finde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.560", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Atomausstieg in Deutschland ist nach wie vor nicht vollendet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.360", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist auch eine Frage der Glaubw\u00fcrdigkeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.200", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er muss vollendet werden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.160", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn nach wie vor sind die Uranfabriken in Gronau und Lingen vom Atomausstieg ausgenommen und d\u00fcrfen weiterhin den Brennstoff f\u00fcr Atomkraftwerke in aller Welt exportieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.440", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch f\u00fcr die maroden Reaktoren Tihange und Doel in Belgien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.800", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die heute schon zur Sprache gebracht worden sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist skandal\u00f6s und muss beendet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.800", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will noch eines zu den Urananreicherungsanlagen sagen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da bin ich ganz bei Nina Scheer\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.720", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Urananreicherungsanlage in Gronau ist janusk\u00f6pfig: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.880", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einerseits kann dort angereichertes Uran f\u00fcr Atomkraftwerke produziert werden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.360", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf der anderen Seite kann mit dieser Technologie Uran derma\u00dfen angereichert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.200", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass damit Atombomben hergestellt werden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.760", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen muss sie meines Erachtens genauso wie die Brenn\u00adelementefabrik in Lingen definitiv geschlossen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.800", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das fordern wir in unseren Antr\u00e4gen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.960", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das muss entsprechend umgesetzt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.800", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen herzlichen Dank f\u00fcr die Aufmerksamkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.000", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion hat das Wort der Kollege Michael Kie\u00dfling."
   ]
  }
 ]
}